Titolo: Hoops (1986 video game)

Anno: 1986

Descrizione: Hoops is a college basketball-themed 1986 video game published by Hoops for IBM PC and compatible computers written by Jeff Sagarin and Wayne Winston, with additional coding done by Jeff Klopfenstein. Billy Packer, the CBS basketball analyst, also provided defensive rating statistics for the game. The publisher ("Hoops") was run by Sagarin and Winston, and the game was sold only by mail order.